{"tid":2235483,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"馬鞍山火人案夫婦被指爆粗　早前被裁公眾地方擾亂秩序罪名不成立 司法機構接投訴 律政司已提上訴","createTime":"2020-10-08T17:07:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-09T12:54:00.000Z","uid":240362,"like":5,"dislike":236,"uniUserReply":73,"replies":[{"pid":"20f0d2999c17cb3129a24fdb0003335d52883190","tid":2235483,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T17:07:20.000Z","msg":"去年11月有地盤挖泥工人在馬鞍山追趕涉嫌破壞港鐵站的黑衣人，追至附近天橋時與途人爭執，遭淋潑易燃液體及點火，全身着火。一對夫婦被指當日事前在場喧嘩及爆粗，事後遭控以在公眾地方擾亂秩序罪。案件早前審結，裁判官林希維裁定夫婦兩人脫罪。律政司今日表示，已根據《裁判官條例》以案件呈述方式提出上訴。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201008/R6GQMOEXINGJXLUKX2RWB6XWAI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201008%2FR6GQMOEXINGJXLUKX2RWB6XWAI%2F&d=bW%2FimIc%2BBhL52Hx1BZusrz11NNBcSSu27FcfjCvRQ4I%3D&h=4ddc8e69\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201008%2FR6GQMOEXINGJXLUKX2RWB6XWAI%2F&h=bcc26379\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201008/R6GQMOEXINGJXLUKX2RWB6XWAI/</a>"},{"pid":"7431390a1073a1f678f6efcad5f84a128116e785","tid":2235483,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T17:09:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3af652ae95fb6d8792e07c9eaac27f2aea7f23a3","tid":2235483,"uid":22893,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T17:09:22.000Z","msg":"OnL9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5f21980e5599703ef77b79425717cecd198c4f4","tid":2235483,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T17:10:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" clas